  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966540/extras/1f22e66eaf95d84e1bd37c6417863b10.avif?t=1568798836\" width=616 height=196 /></span><br><br>They say that child’s imagination is pure and innocent.<br>But what if said imagination becomes a nightmare?<br><br>Play as a youngling surviving through the night in the pixelated horror. Your once beloved teddy bear had come to life and became conscious.<br>Wander around your bedroom, searching for clues to unravel the story - but keep a close eye on the room, as each hour it slowly changes.<br><br>Listen close for when it comes, scare the teddy away with your flashlight, and don’t forget to check under the bed for monsters….<br>Is this nightmare real? Is your bedtime over?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966540/extras/8b3a271064302283160848d1a65af449.poster.avif?t=1568798836\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966540/extras/8b3a271064302283160848d1a65af449.webm?t=1568798836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966540/extras/8b3a271064302283160848d1a65af449.mp4?t=1568798836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pixel-art design<br></li><li>Simple controls<br></li><li>Randomized AI<br></li><li>Free Roam<br></li><li>Ever Changing World</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966540/extras/564c24f3f8527aad68f75f74529163a3.poster.avif?t=1568798836\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966540/extras/564c24f3f8527aad68f75f74529163a3.webm?t=1568798836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/966540/extras/564c24f3f8527aad68f75f74529163a3.mp4?t=1568798836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
